Why AGPL-3.0
------------

This project patches MinerU's internals at runtime (see lib/patch_mineru.py)
and is therefore a derivative work of MinerU. MinerU is licensed under
AGPL-3.0, so this project inherits AGPL-3.0. The license is forced by
upstream, not chosen.

If you run a modified version of this software as a network service, AGPL
§13 requires you to offer the corresponding source code to your users.


